LANE-MORSE LUMBER COMPANY, Inc., a corporation, v. UNITED STATES FIDELITY AND GUARANTY COMPANY, a corporation. No. 6492. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Nov. 3, 1960. Edwin Langley, Muskogee, Okl., for appellant. Fite & Robinson, Muskogee, Okl., for appellee.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and’ BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellant.
